Package org.jscripter.emu.gc

Re-compilation helping classes for emulation of garbage collection and finalization.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
DFS An internal abstract base class for DOM-enabled depth-first-search object visitors emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript.
DFSCollector An internal class for DOM-enabled depth-first-search garbage collectors emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript.
DFSMarker An internal class for DOM-enabled depth-first-search garbage markers emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript.
DFSReviver An internal class for DOM-enabled depth-first-search object revivers emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript.
DFSSearcher An internal class for DOM-enabled depth-first-search garbage searchers emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript.
DFSSweeper An internal class for DOM-enabled depth-first-search garbage sweepers emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript.
GC An internal abstract base class for DOM-enabled visitors emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript.
GCDOM An internal base class of DOM object visitors emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript for DOM implementations.
 

Package org.jscripter.emu.gc Description

Re-compilation helping classes for emulation of garbage collection and finalization.

These classes and interfaces are not for JS applications but only used internally by JS re-complier implementations for emulation.
